title: Taking The Limits Off of God | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Taking The Limits Off of God | Joel Osteen
description:
If you want to see God's blessings, you have to line your thoughts up with God's. Don't let a negative mentality keep you from the new things He wants to do in your life. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
